text: Max Happle (born 26 October 1914, date of death unknown) was a Swiss diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Swiss male divers Category:Olympic divers of Switzerland Category:Divers at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
